title: Executive Order 3452-Chuckekanzie
content: It is hereby ordered that the east half of the northwest quarter of section twenty-nine, township eight south, range twenty-one east of the Mount Diablo meridian, in California, withdrawn for Indian use by Executive Order 2023, dated August 14, 1914, be, and the same is hereby, restored to its former status.
citation: Warren G. Harding, Executive Order 3452-Chuckekanzie Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/277259
